OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy in
OL,6,Fthe west with patchy rain and coastal
OL,7,Ffog but a warm and bright evening in
OL,8,Fthe east. Rain in the west will turn
OL,9,Fheavier overnight with some spreading
OL,10,Feastwards.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FSome brightness at first in
OL,13,Fthe east. Otherwise, cloudy with
OL,14,Foutbreaks of rain, heavy at times.
OL,15,FBecoming drier towards the west coast
OL,16,Fin the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
