OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,6,FOccasionally heavy overnight rain
OL,7,Fclearing. Saturday cooler, mainly
OL,8,Fcloudy but west coast brightening up.
OL,9,FSunday and Monday dry with some
OL,10,Fsunshine at times, especially Monday,
OL,11,Fand turning warmer again.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
